description.0: Dr. Druid catches on to Ghost Rider’s rage after Johnny Blaze makes a personal discovery about Roxanne.
description.1: The Eternals at last reveal their existenc to the mortal world! But soon after, two of their own are attacked by a mysterious new foe! How many Eternals does it take to defeat DROMEDAN?! The world may never know...!
description.2: Hulk battles the Bi-Beast! And the stakes have never been higher!
description.3: In this issue: Iron Man takes on the Jack of Hearts and the merciless minions of Midas! Plus: Madame Masque joins Midas in an evil attempt to sabotage Stark Internationals. Can Iron Man manage to evade all these attacks?
description.4: After mourning the death of John Nedley, James-Michael and Dian run away to the mountains of upstate New York.
description.5: Loki knows there's only one way he can keep Asgard's throne- he must have Odin executed! Can Loki fulfill his dubious plans with the help of his allies Executioner and Enchantress?
description.6: What if Captain America hadn't vanished during World War Two?
description.7: After being transported through a star-gate by Phoenix, the X-Men find themselves on an ancient planet that is home to the M'Kraan Crystal, surrounded by several members of the Shi'ar Imperial Guard serving the evil Emperor D'Ken.
description.8: Klaw and Molecule Man ambush the Baxter Building- along with its residents! Can the team battle the intruders...with Mister Fantastic powerless to help?
description.10: Carol Danvers as Ms. Marvel and Spider-Man uncover the source of the Super-Skrull's remarkable power. And it's a far-out tale from outer space!
description.11: While Dyna-Mite tries to take down Adolf Hitler, the Invaders take on the combined might of Master Man and Warrior Woman!
description.14: Howard the Duck is captured by the mysterious Dr. Bong, who is looking to perform experiments on Howard. Just who is Dr. Bong and what does he want
description.15: A world overrun by giant insects! Adapting H. G. Wells' novel The Food of the Gods and How It Came to Earth.
description.16: Obi-Wan vs Darth Vader! Plus, can Han and Luke rescue Leia?
description.17: An explosive conclusion to the Molten Man saga! Barely recovered from his battle with Molten Man, Spider-Man must lunge into action to save Liz Allan. In a battle to the death, who will emerge victorious?
description.18: The Lethal Legion is back and demanding blood. Featuring Whirlwind, Power Man, and the Living Laser.
description.19: Cap and Falcon take on the Night Flyer, who has in his use, a dangerous force called "the Power."
description.26: Her apartment destroyed, her life hounded by the villainous Deathbird, and her freedom once again taken away by A.I.M.! But if Carol thought THAT was a bad day, wait until she sees who crashes in to her rescue!
description.28: Sandman, under the control of Yellow Claw! Can Nova defeat the powerful duo of Sandman and Claw…and save his classmate?
description.30: Spider-Woman’s shocked to her senses after an explosion wipes away Hydra’s mind control. Exactly how long has Spider-Woman been under Hydra’s influence? Alicia Masters is the test subject in one of Hydra’s shadowy experiments. Will Ben Grimm recognize the woman he loves by the time Hydra’s done with her? This is one ending too horrifying to miss!
description.31: Our space born super hero must find a way to defeat Phaedor!
description.32: The return of Molten Man! After Liz Allan acts uncharacteristically, Peter decides to do some investigating as Spider-Man. What dark truths will Spider-Man uncover about Liz Allan's half-brother? And why is J. Jonah Jameson acting so strangely around Marla Madison? Plus, Rocket Racer gives Spidey a run for his money...literally!
description.33: Three members of The Defenders versus Iron Man! Plus, Hercules returns to earth accompanied by an arch-nemesis with a grudge of divine proportions. Featuring Typhon!
description.34: In a SHIELD-run hospital, a heavily bandaged man known only as the Defector is attacked by Night Flyer. Still wounded from his last battle, Cap must step in to save the mysterious man.
description.35: Swarm's unbelievable origin revealed! Iceman and Darkstar have been captured by the bee-witching villain, and if they don't help Swarm unleash his Queen Bee...all of Los Angeles will be stung!
description.36: The Millennium Falcon is captured by the Death Star, which has just destroyed another planet!
description.37: Daredevil's on the trail of the mysterious figure at the head of the recent criminal activity, but he'll have to contend with Death-Stalker first!
description.38: It's an all-out brawl as Sersi and Ikaris face off with a robot Hulk, who's been mega-charged with cosmic power!! Can even two mighty Eternals stand up to this deadly doppelganger?
description.39: The Hulk is taken unawares when apprehended by S.H.I.E.L.D.! What mysterious force is wreaking havoc inside the S.H.I.E.L.D. chopper?
description.40: Iron Man and the Frankenstein Monster must put their differences aside to save Victoria Frankenstein from the Dreadknight! Can Iron Man align himself with the likes of evil to save the day? Find out as Iron Man continues his most spooky adventure yet!
description.41: In the ravages of battle, Volstagg gains new abilities! Is the warrior now strong enough to defeat the Odin-beast? Meanwhile, an unpleasant surprise awaits Thor in Asgard's throne room.
description.42: Dracula's vengeance tour continues as he grieves for his lost son.
description.43: The 'treasonous' Agatha Harkness is sentenced to public execution! The Fantastic Four are confronted by Salem's Seven- does the team stand a chance?
description.47: Jules Verne's Master of the World is adapted in stunning detail!
description.49: Spidey lends a web-slinging hand to the Human Torch after the hero is overcome by the Super-Skrull!
description.50: Union Jack is back! And he's just in time to save the Invaders from execution!
description.52: In this very special issue, Steve Gerber presents his look behind the curtain of the comic book industry.
description.56: She escaped the clutches of A.I.M., but when Carol returns for payback, the trail turns mysteriously cold! But that's the least of her problems, as the man-monster Grotesk is back for another fight! Can Carol survive against the beast that defeated her once before?
description.60: Spider-Woman gets the drop on Thing! But why is she aligned with Hydra? Ben Grimm suspects foul play and reaches out to Scotland Yard, and Nick Fury, for assistance. But before Spider-Woman’s apprehended, Alicia is kidnapped! Woe be to her kidnapper- Thing’s on the chase and ready to clobber!
description.62: Captain Marvel and Adam Warlock aid the Avengers in their fight against Thanos. The fate of the universe hangs in the balance as the heroes race to destroy Thanos' artificial Soul Gem.
description.64: The Champions guest-star! The West Coast super hero team joins Iron Man in his battle against M.O.D.O.K. and the many hordes of A.I.M. A Champion falls amidst the fighting- but who?
description.65: The first appearance of the new Union Jack!
description.67: Howard has finally shut out the voices in his head, but Howard and Beverly find themselves stranded on a mysterious island populated by humanoid animals - what will Howard and Beverly encounter next!?
description.68: The villainous Malice sets the Hollywood Wax Museum ablaze! Ghost Rider responds by dousing him in hellfire...
description.69: Ikaris, Makarri and Sersi head to earth to discover the cause of a mysterious flare of cosmic energy, but first they'll have to face...the Incredible Hulk!?
description.70: How is Jack of Hearts different from the rest of Hulk's foes? And what's setting off Hulk's murderous rage this time?
description.71: The most unexpected foe of the year! The Armored Avenger battles for his life against the monster of Frankenstein!
description.73: The Soul Survivors have the God of Thunder captive...and they're using the All-Father Odin to gain power! Will this be the final demise of the Asgardian King? Or will it be the rebirth of something far greater?
description.74: Something has happened to Son of Dracula! And his father is looking for vengeance!
description.75: How different would our world have wound up if the Invaders never disbanded? Where would Cap, Namor, the Torch and the rest of the team be now?
description.76: Just moments after the X-Men chased Erik the Red through space, Professor X, Misty Knight and Jean Grey's parents are confronted by Firelord.
description.77: Franklin and Agatha's location is traced to New Salem! But when the FF arrive, they become spellbound by the supernatural locals!
description.86: Continuing the adaptatation of a New Hope!  Luke and Ben solicit the help of Han Solo and Chewie to rescue Leia!
description.87: Spider-Man and Nova team-up to find the killer of Nova's uncle. Will the two heroes be able to defeat the super-powered menace of Photon?
description.88: Ultron has unleashed his own brand of havoc against the Avengers. See the team disassemble in the chaos. Who will fall? And who will rise from the ashes?
description.89: As the Red Skull's deteriorating headquarters crumbles around them, Sharon Carter and a blinded Cap must find a way to escape before it's too late.
description.90: Adapting one of the most famous Gothic horrors of all time! The tale of scientist Victor Frankenstein… and the monster he gave birth to!
description.92: The Thing and Alicia have safely delivered Deathlok to London- but where is Professor Kort, the man who may be able to save the cyborg’s life? A missing person case leads to a team-up between The Thing and Shang-Chi…that is, if the two heroes can set aside initial misunderstandings!
description.94: Ms. Marvel...defeated!? Captured by A.I.M., Carol has to fight her way to freedom! But can even she defeat a Mental Organism Designed Only for Killing?
description.95: Mar-Vell locks horns with the menace of MERCURIO, the four dimensional man!
description.98: It's an all-insect team as Spidey joins forces with Yellowjacket and the Wasp! But when one of the trio falls, will the other two stay on the hero's path...or go down a dark road for revenge?
description.99: Captain America teams up with the Destroyer to free an American in the clutches of the Nazis.

9.text: Spider-Man is accustomed to saving lives, but what happens when someone saves his? With his savior now slowly dying from diving in front of a chemical truck, can Spidey return the favor and find an antidote in time?

12.text: Strange, Clea, and Wong return to Earth and discover the planet's terrain has changed and its people are now anthropomorphic beings!

13.text: Hulk must protect Namor from a mob when the Atlantean royal arrives in New York City.

20.text: 2,000 feet above modern-day London, Shang-Chi duels a foe from the past!

23.text: Zzzax, a being of ‘living lightening’, is resurrected! Cage must defend a young woman from Zzzax’s attack…all while keeping the foe at arm’s length!

25.text: Come join the epic fantasy of Tyndall the elf, lost creature of Klarn! In this quest through Weirdworld, Tyndall witnesses a female elf hatch from an egg. Enter Velanna, courageous companion and fighter for good! Tyndall and Velanna join forces to uncover the mystery of their forgotten pasts.

26.text: Her apartment destroyed, her life hounded by the villainous Deathbird, and her freedom once again taken away by A.I.M.! But if Carol thought THAT was a bad day, wait until she sees who crashes in to her rescue!

27.text: X-Men & Iron Fist Team-Up! Marvel’s mighty mutants take down the Bushmaster and Steel Serpent in Iron Fist’s final issue. Legendary X-Men scribe Chris Claremont delivers powerful storytelling…and punches!

28.text: Sandman, under the control of Yellow Claw! Can Nova defeat the powerful duo of Sandman and Claw…and save his classmate?

29.text: The Prince of Wakanda takes off on a new adventure! With Abner Little in company, Black Panther begins his quest for a sacred water-skin. But will Zanda’s reckless behavior derail the mission?

30.text: Spider-Woman’s shocked to her senses after an explosion wipes away Hydra’s mind control. Exactly how long has Spider-Woman been under Hydra’s influence? Alicia Masters is the test subject in one of Hydra’s shadowy experiments. Will Ben Grimm recognize the woman he loves by the time Hydra’s done with her? This is one ending too horrifying to miss!

31.text: Our space born super hero must find a way to defeat Phaedor!

37.text: Daredevil's on the trail of the mysterious figure at the head of the recent criminal activity, but he'll have to contend with Death-Stalker first!

44.text: We continue with Spidey fighting the White Tiger, but is this menace really who he says he is? And, will the college protests of Empire State University ever be resolved?

51.text: Nick Fury offers Jack Norriss a job at S.H.I.E.L.D; Tani is taken to the headquarters of a secret project in Russia.

53.text: Shang-Chi, Reston and Tarr take on a villain who can mirror several fighting styles from history's best warriors!

56.text: She escaped the clutches of A.I.M., but when Carol returns for payback, the trail turns mysteriously cold! But that's the least of her problems, as the man-monster Grotesk is back for another fight! Can Carol survive against the beast that defeated her once before?

58.text: Richard Rider’s uncle has been murdered! And the suspect is…Peter Parker?!

59.text: Doctor Doom makes good on his promise to Namor and returns to Atlantis to aid its comatose citizens. But when Warlord Krang, longtime enemy to Namor, crashes their arrival, Doom must sweep into super villain action! Namor and Doc Doom, (finally on the same side), versus Warlord Krang!

60.text: Spider-Woman gets the drop on Thing! But why is she aligned with Hydra? Ben Grimm suspects foul play and reaches out to Scotland Yard, and Nick Fury, for assistance. But before Spider-Woman’s apprehended, Alicia is kidnapped! Woe be to her kidnapper- Thing’s on the chase and ready to clobber!

61.text: The Defenders square off against Scorpio’s LMD, (Life Model Decoy), army! With the aid of Hulk and Moon Knight, the team manages to free Nighthawk. After destroying Scorpio’s army, the team is horrified to discover that Scorpio has taken his own life!

63.text: Spider-Man is joined by the Wasp to take down a thermodynamic villain who claims to have already laid waste to Yellowjacket!

66.text: Apalla reveals to Doctor Strange the Creators' plan to create a new universe by using the Wheel of Change!

78.text: The flames of protest! Peter's Empire State University classmates are beyond angered that due to budget cuts, all night classes have been canceled. What type of riots will ensue?

79.text: The Inhumans face a final battle, and they'll need help from the Incredible Hulk!

80.text: Shang-Chi races against the clock to save himself from certain death!

83.text: Power Man faces distraction after distraction as he races against the clock to find and destroy Gideon Mace’s atomic bomb. Read for the major twist of an ending!

84.text: Charlie-27 discovers Drydock, the Federation Starship where he did his basic training. When the ship goes rogue, who better than Charlie to save the rest of the Guardians?

91.text: Black Panther’s locked in mystical battle with the Collectors! But first? A timely escape from King Solomon’s tomb. Panther and Abner discover Zanda’s loyalties are with her kingdom- is she a friend or foe?

92.text: The Thing and Alicia have safely delivered Deathlok to London- but where is Professor Kort, the man who may be able to save the cyborg’s life? A missing person case leads to a team-up between The Thing and Shang-Chi…that is, if the two heroes can set aside initial misunderstandings!

93.text: Before Moon Knight can alert the Defenders on the whereabouts of Scorpio, Nighthawk is taken hostage. Meanwhile, the team attempts to convince an unruly Hulk to fight for them. With a friend in danger, and time running out, what measures will the Defenders take to get Hulk on their side?

94.text: Ms. Marvel...defeated!? Captured by A.I.M., Carol has to fight her way to freedom! But can even she defeat a Mental Organism Designed Only for Killing?

95.text: Mar-Vell locks horns with the menace of MERCURIO, the four dimensional man!

96.text: Richard Rider’s memories have been erased! Will he recover in time to stop the Sphinx?
